OL,3,CBradford factory destroyed by fire
OL,5,FA huge fire has torn through a factory
OL,6,Fin Bradford.
OL,8,FResidents living in the BD4 area area
OL,9,Fwere asked to keep doors and windows
OL,10,Fclosed following the incident in
OL,11,FBowling Park Close.
OL,13,FFifteen crews were involved in
OL,14,Ftackling the blaze at its height at
OL,15,Faround 10pm on Wednesday, 29 April.
OL,17,FWest Yorkshire Fire and Rescue Service
OL,18,Fasked the public to avoid the area.
