OL,3,CBradford factory destroyed by fire
OL,5,FIn an update shared on Thursday
OL,6,Fevening, the fire service confirmed
OL,7,Fone crew and one engine remain at the
OL,8,Fscene.
OL,10,FA spokesperson said: "The fire is out
OL,11,Fbut firefighters are continuing to
OL,12,Fdamp down.
OL,14,F"No cause has been ascertained as yet,
OL,15,Fdue to awaiting a structural engineer
OL,16,Fto check the safety of the building
OL,17,Ffollowing the fire."
